na Mignosa, Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">··</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Εὐβουλ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Εὐβουλ\"><span data-text=\"Εὐβουλ\">ΕΥΒΟΥΛ</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Τ · υἱὸς · Σεουε͂ρος\"><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Τ\">Τ</span>·Υ·<span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"cognomen\" data-text=\"Σεουε͂ρος\">ΣΕΟΥΕΡ[..]</span></span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>[....].ΚΑΛΟΣ&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]Υ·ΣΠΕΡΚΙΑ[...]<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀφρικανὸς\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"cognomen\" data-text=\"Ἀφρικανὸς\">ΑΦΡΙΚ[....]</span></span><br id=\"al7-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span data-text=\"ς\">Σ</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div>"
